{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_0138FZg2pF8Ucfmchw7Jsboq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. The implementation was already in place — the only issue was a duplicate `FitnessRecord` type definition in `types.go` that conflicted with the one in `fitness.go`. I renamed the `types.go` version to `RunScoreRecord` (since it's a different concept — a simple score record for population tracking) and updated its tests accordingly.\n\nThe `fitness.go` file contains all requested functions:\n- **EvaluateRun** — extracts metrics (success/fail, retry count, duration) from `domain.Run`\n- **RecordFitness** / **LoadFitness** — JSONL I/O to fitness file\n- **AggregateFitness** — groups by candidate, computes success rate + efficiency\n- **ComputeParetoFront** — returns non-dominated set\n- **Dominates** — multi-objective comparison (success rate, efficiency)\n\nThe `fitness_test.go` file has comprehensive table-driven tests including known Pareto fronts.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1143,"cache_read_input_tokens":32008,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1143},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a6717437-3589-4939-a51b-a20f6016956f","uuid":"cf9de40d-5b43-4b79-9aa1-3e03b137148a"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":188794,"duration_api_ms":135104,"num_turns":18,"result":"All tests pass. The implementation was already in place — the only issue was a duplicate `FitnessRecord` type definition in `types.go` that conflicted with the one in `fitness.go`. I renamed the `types.go` version to `RunScoreRecord` (since it's a different concept — a simple score record for population tracking) and updated its tests accordingly.\n\nThe `fitness.go` file contains all requested functions:\n- **EvaluateRun** — extracts metrics (success/fail, retry count, duration) from `domain.Run`\n- **RecordFitness** / **LoadFitness** — JSONL I/O to fitness file\n- **AggregateFitness** — groups by candidate, computes success rate + efficiency\n- **ComputeParetoFront** — returns non-dominated set\n- **Dominates** — multi-objective comparison (success rate, efficiency)\n\nThe `fitness_test.go` file has comprehensive table-driven tests including known Pareto fronts.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"a6717437-3589-4939-a51b-a20f6016956f","total_cost_usd":0.46163755,"usage":{"input_tokens":14,"cache_creation_input_tokens":24603,"cache_read_input_tokens":310535,"output_tokens":3124,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":24603,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":14,"outputTokens":3124,"cacheReadInputTokens":310535,"cacheCreationInputTokens":24603,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.3872062499999999,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":40,"outputTokens":3156,"cacheReadInputTokens":151613,"cacheCreationInputTokens":34760,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.07443129999999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uui